## 4. Tickets

This is the most important resource in the entire API.

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Role Required |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/tickets` | List all tickets for the tenant with filters | agent, supervisor |
| GET | `/tickets/:id` | Get full ticket details | agent, supervisor |
| POST | `/tickets` | Create a new ticket (from any channel) | agent, supervisor |
| PATCH | `/tickets/:id` | Update ticket status, tier, or assignment | agent, supervisor |
| GET | `/tickets/:id/messages` | Get all messages for a ticket | agent, supervisor |
| POST | `/tickets/:id/messages` | Add a new message to a ticket | agent, supervisor |
| GET | `/tickets/:id/escalations` | Get escalation history for a ticket | agent, supervisor |
| POST | `/tickets/:id/escalate` | Escalate a ticket to the next tier | agent, supervisor |

**GET /tickets — Query Parameters**
```
?status=open
?tier=tier_2
?channel=email
?assigned_agent_id=uuid
?language=ar
?page=1&limit=20
```

**POST /tickets — Request Body**
```json
{
  "customer_id": "uuid",
  "channel": "chat",
  "tier": "tier_1",
  "issue_type": "password_reset",
  "subject": "Cannot log into my account",
  "language": "en"
}
```

**POST /tickets/:id/escalate — Request Body**
```json
{
  "from_tier": "tier_1",
  "to_tier": "tier_2",
  "escalation_reason": "Identity verification passed but reset link delivery failed after 2 attempts.",
  "context_snapshot": {
    "messages": [],
    "actions_taken": [],
    "customer_summary": {}
  }
}
```

**PATCH /tickets/:id — Request Body**
```json
{
  "status": "resolved",
  "resolution_summary": "Password reset email sent successfully.",
  "assigned_agent_id": "uuid"
}
```

