## What This API Deliberately Leaves Out for MVP

- Webhook endpoints for Shopify, Stripe, and Zendesk (integration scope deferred)
- WebSocket endpoints for real-time ticket updates (use polling on the frontend for MVP)
- File attachment endpoints for ticket messages
- Notification delivery endpoints (email/WhatsApp sending handled by backend services internally, not exposed as API routes)
